1. Overview

The license_source collection stores metadata about licensing authorities across different scopes (Global, National, State). It is designed to support license verification, compliance checks, and reporting use cases.


2. Objectives

Maintain a centralized repository of license authorities

Support efficient lookup and filtering by scope and geography

Ensure data consistency using schema validation

Optimize performance using appropriate indexing


📌 3. Primary Use Cases

Lookup license authority using HON

Filter records by:

SCOPE

COUNTRY

STATE

LICENSE_TYPE

Regulatory compliance checks

Reporting and analytics
